USA: Hoechst's Allegra antihistamine available.Hoechst's Allegra antihistamine available.Hoechst Marion Roussel said Tuesday that Allegra, its non-sedating antihistamine, is now available by prescription in the United States.The drug, which treats seasonal allergy symptoms, was approved for marketing on July 25 by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration.Allegra is priced 15 percent less than similar treatments, according to a statement by the company.Hoechst Marion Roussel is a unit of Hoechst AG.	     -- Chicago newsdesk, 312 408-8787